supplementary-material.p: Representative flow cytometry gating for cell sorting of peripheral lymph nodes. Parent gating strategy for the flow cytometric sorting of day 5 and day 27 post-ZIKV infection LN samples for analysis of cellular infection status by RT-PCR. A representative staining profile from the ZIKV cohort is shown. Live, singlet leukocytes were sorted into T cell (CD3 +), B cell (CD20 +), or myeloid cell (CD11b +) populations.
